4.2 Physical Analysis of EFF Upper Limit

98.04% is not a design deficiency — it is the theoretical upper limit set by the Landauer physical limit.

Landauer limit: E_min = kT * ln2 ~ 1.38e-23 * 300 * 0.693 ~ 2.87 zJ/bit

The remaining ~1.96% irreversible energy corresponds to each irreversible logical bit erasure. This is a manifestation of the Second Law of Thermodynamics in information processing. No computing system can break this limit unless fully reversible computation is achieved.

4.3 Physical Significance of Resonance State

(1) All four islands online: total stored energy at maximum
(2) Energy in ENG CORE forms a circulation loop among the four islands
(3) Clock at 500MHz equivalent; low photonic delay keeps timing margin positive
